videoSnippet.title: Who Needs a Queen? | Praggu vs Eljanov | Isle of Man (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Rameshbabu Praggnanandhaa vs Pavel Eljanov
Isle of Man Open Tournament, Round 3
23 Oct 2018.
